<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">وقال آخر:</span> <span class="c4">[الكامل]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>ولقد غَرِضْتُ إلى تَناصُفِ وَجْهِها ... غَرَضَ المُحِبِّ إلى الحَبيبِ الغَائِبِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وغَسَّانُ:</span> اسمُ رَجُل.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">وغَسَّانُ:</span> ماءٌ معروف،<span class="c5"> قال حَسَّان:</span> <span class="c4">[البسيط]</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>الأَزْدُ نِسْبَتُنَا والماءُ غَسَّانُ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">ويُقال:</span> لَسْتُ مِنْ غَسَّانِه،<span class="c5"> أي:</span> لَسْتُ مِنْ ضَرْبهِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">ويُقال:</span> غَسَلْت الثوبَ بالماء غَسْلاً.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">وغَسَل الرَّجُلُ المرأةَ غَسْلاً:</span> نَكَحَها.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وفَحْلُ غُسَلَةٌ، وغُسَلٌ،<span class="c5"> وغَسِيلٌ:</span> يُكْثِرُ الضِّراب ولا يُلْقِحُ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">والغَضِيض الطَّرْفِ:</span> المُسْتَرْخِي الأجفان.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">والغَضِيضُ:</span> الطَّلْعُ إذا بدا.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">والغُوطَة:</span> بِدِمَشْقَ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">وكلُّ وَهْدَةٍ:</span> غُوطَة.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c5">والغَوْطُ:</span> الثَّرِيد.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>